{"tid":2108521,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想問一下勞工法例","createTime":"2020-07-14T15:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T15:36:41.000Z","uid":228082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc69d936567029e2a8cfb9b74d20b7f2fb62624","tid":2108521,"uid":228082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"各位師兄師姐，而家情況係咁，我係sales 一名，公司啱啱出咗一個新嘅Policy, 每一個月要做一次審核，佢定左一啲條件要我哋去achieve, 從而在去評定一個grading , A+,A,B,C,D咁，如拎C就要扣相應嘅人工from 底薪，當然呢個新嘅policy 佢之前份合約一定冇寫明，佢而家突然間+1條新條款，係勞工法例上係咪可以容許？<br />\n<br />\n當然呢啲新嘅規矩係sale result嘅指標，但新policy係非常不合理，我地係做project sales嘅，一年好大可能係做1到2張大project 就meet or over achieve target , 但如咁去計，我係比佢扣左足足11個月，得一個月好叻仔over achieve yearly target比倒bonus , 但肯定係補唔翻果11個扣左果d。。。<br />\n<br />\n各位幫幫手比下意見🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻"},{"pid":"ab8001acd5c2bd8148804c5f568d3db7b297274c","tid":2108521,"uid":311540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:30:16.000Z","msg":"搵新工"},{"pid":"e63cd3802daed42c0521a2d15f0b804dec7d60b0","tid":2108521,"uid":362909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/employmentDisputes/all.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.clic.org.hk%2Ftc%2Ftopics%2FemploymentDisputes%2Fall.shtml&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuBD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=61d5d37b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.clic.org.hk/tc/topics/employmentDisputes/all.shtml</a><br />\n可參考第5及第6點"}]}